<p>
    <div class="l-example katex-my-1">
    \( \sum_{n=1}^{\infty} u_{n}(x)=f(x)+\lambda \int_{0}^{x} K(x, t)\left(\sum_{n=1}^{\infty} u_{n}(t)\right) d t \)
    </div>
</p>
<p>
    <div class="l-example katex-my-1">
    \( u_{0}(x)+u_{1}(x)+u_{2}(x)+\ldots=f(x)+\lambda \int_{0}^{x} K(x, t) u_{0}(t) d t+\lambda \int_{0}^{x} K(x, t) u_{1}(t) d t+\ldots \)
    </div>
